OL,3,CHow to save someone's life with a
OL,4,Cbleed kit
OL,6,FHundreds of life-saving bleed kits
OL,7,Fhave been installed across the West
OL,8,FCountry - but would you know how to
OL,9,Fuse one?
OL,11,FLike CPR, it's the sort of thing many
OL,12,Fof us would like the chance to
OL,13,Fpractice, before we're in a life and
OL,14,Fdeath situation.
OL,16,FAnti-knife crime campaigner Leanne
OL,17,FReynolds said that "anyone can use" a
OL,18,Fbleed kit.
