OL,3,CHow to save someone's life with a
OL,4,Cbleed kit
OL,6,F"You don't need any training and you
OL,7,Fcan stop the bleed while you wait for
OL,8,Fan ambulance", she said.
OL,10,F"These kits have been designed for
OL,11,Fpublic access and while you're on the
OL,12,F999 call they'll direct you through
OL,13,Fthe contents and advise you how to
OL,14,Fstop the bleed."
OL,16,FShe has worked with the Daniel Baird
OL,17,Ffoundation to get the kits installed
OL,18,Facross Bristol and Bath. Dan was just
OL,19,F26 when he was fatally stabbed in
OL,20,FBirmingham in 2017.
