OL,6,FLast month, , Bristol. Leanne attended
OL,7,Fa and said people were "shattered" by
OL,8,Fthe news.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country
OL,11,Fnearly two weeks on, she added: "I
OL,12,Fthink the shock and devastation is
OL,13,Fstill there.
OL,15,F"Tina Bond from Bristol City Council
OL,16,Fhas led a partnership of all the youth
OL,17,Forganisations to actually safeguard
OL,18,Fand look after all the individuals and
OL,19,Fmake sure they have trauma counselling.
