OL,3,CHow to save someone's life with a
OL,4,Cbleed kit
OL,6,F"We have activities for young people
OL,7,Fto get them off the streets."
OL,9,FThe kits can vary in design, but each
OL,10,Fone typically contains two trauma
OL,11,Fdressings, two haemostatic dressings
OL,12,Fand a tourniquet.
OL,14,FSome also have a chest shield which
OL,15,Fallows the injured person to breathe
OL,16,Fmore easily after sustaining a torso
OL,17,Fwound.
